import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { UserDto } from '../dto/UserDto'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { ENDPOINTS } from '../rest-endpoint'; @Component({ selector: 'app-manage', templateUrl: './manage.component.html', styleUrls: ['./manage.component.css'] }) export class ManageComponent implements OnInit{ existingUsers: UserDto [] = [] constructor (private http:HttpClient){} ngOnInit(): void { this.http.get(ENDPOINTS.GETALL).subscribe( (data) => { this.existingUsers = data; console.log(this.existingUsers); } ) } }
